// React component: In react everything is a component like a header ,footer etc.
// there are two types of components in react.
// class based components: Old way of writing code.Nobody uses class based components.
// functional components: New way of writing code.Everybody uses functional based components now a days..
// React functional component is just a JS functional component.
// A normal js function which returns react element (or) JSX is called functional componenet.
// for an reactelement we render like this root.render(name).
// for a react componenet we render like this root.render(<name of the comonent/>).
//component inside a component is called component composition.